(this was written for Windows)

ART.src  demonstrates competitive pattern learning.

All patterns are learned in a single pass through
the program. go to eeedisplays a parameter-editing screen.
When you set the vigilance parameter crit to a 
negative value, ART functionality is suppressed. 
Watch the resulting changes in the template-norm 
time history). The templates must now re-learn some
of the patterns in each new pass.
